Original Pipeline

  • Total stage time: 100 ps
  • Total cycle time (including storage): 100 + 20 = 120 ps
  • Throughput: 1 / 120 ps 8.33 Giga instructions/sec

Subdividing Each Stage into 3 Substages

  • Substage time: 100 / 3 = 33.33 ps
  • Cycle time: 33.33 + 20 = 53.33 ps
  • Throughput: 1 / 53.33 ps 18.75 Giga instructions/sec

Subdividing Each Stage into 5 Substages

  • Substage time: 100 / 5 = 20 ps
  • Cycle time: 20 + 20 = 40 ps
  • Throughput: 1 / 40 ps = 25 Giga instructions/sec
